name: Dessert Blockchain
tagline: Discuss the block chain over some tasty treats
body:
### Welcome to the Dessert Block Chain.

Don't know anything about The Blockchain? Neither do we! Come talk with us over ice cream sandwiches. We'll discuss how The Blockchain works, what The Blockchain can do, and how The Blockchain can solve all your problems.

Our first meeting will be held on Thursday, July 7th, 2016 at [Slickables in Tempe, AZ](https://www.google.com/maps/place/Slickables/@33.4233383,-111.9414655,16.87z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x872b08d82b809adf:0xad7bb35a5f53de07!8m2!3d33.4234812!4d-111.9397873).
